### ========================================
### 1. 管理员接口测试 (Admin API)
### ========================================
# 获取所有系统用户列表 (包含老师、学生、管理员)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admins/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-admin-1

### ========================================
### 2. 课程管理接口测试 (Course API)
### ========================================
# 创建一门课程 (传课程名以及任课老师的ID) (建课只能由admin完成)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-admin-1

{
  "name": "高阶软件工程",
  "teacherIds": [2, 3]
}

###
# 查询所有课程 (获取刚创建课程的 courseId, 用于下面的选课，学生和老师也能看)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses
Authorization: token-student-4

###
# 修改课程信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/modify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-admin-1

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "高阶软件工程(修改版)",
  "teacherIds": [2]
}

###
# 查询课程下的所有学生名单 (假设这里填入课程ID => 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/1/students
Authorization: token-student-4

###
# 删除课程
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/courses/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-admin-1

{
  "id": 1
}


### ========================================
### 3. 学生端接口测试 (Student API)
### ========================================
# 小明(学生ID 4) 选修 第1门课(课程ID 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/courses/1/select
Authorization: token-student-4

###
# 查看小明已选的所有课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/my/courses
Authorization: token-student-4

###
# 查看小明的全部成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/my/grades
Authorization: token-student-4

###
# 小明 退课 (课程ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/students/courses/1/drop
Authorization: token-student-4


### ========================================
### 4. 教师端接口测试 (Teacher API)
### ========================================
# 张老师(教师ID 2) 查看自己教的课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers/my/courses
Authorization: token-teacher-2

###
# 张老师给小明(学生ID 4) 的 第1门课打分(95分)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers/grades
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-teacher-2

{
  "studentId": 4,
  "courseId": 1,
  "grade": 95
}

###
# 张老师修改小明的成绩为100分
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers/grades
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: token-teacher-2

{
  "studentId": 4,
  "courseId": 1,
  "grade": 100
}

###
# 张老师查询 第1门课 所有登过的成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teachers/1/grades
Authorization: token-teacher-2


### ========================================
### 5. 用户通用接口测试 (User API)
### ========================================
# 查询小明(ID:4)的个人信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/my/info
Authorization: token-student-4
